des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Kiturami products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our Kiturami Smart app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our Kiturami Smart app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search Kiturami Smart skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable Kiturami Smart skill, and you'll be navigated to Kiturami Smart login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on thermostat
Alexa, turn off thermostat
Alexa, set thermostat to 45 degrees
